Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.05,0:00:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划变得一团乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习→玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.40,0:01:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.73,0:01:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要重写计划表…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如加进学习之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.61,0:01:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  之类的之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学习之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真了不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地定下学习计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.91,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  马克笔的话就不能重写了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.98,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(740,300)}隐藏不住的晒痕与少女心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个占卜相当准的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子你还真喜欢占卜什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过利子你是天秤座的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气超差而且要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候太准了也难办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会要去泳池  要注意水的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在泳池…溺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占什么卜  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的天秤座在吼叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是骗人的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是胡扯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌气睡觉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿幸运色蓝色的衣服运气会不会好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运物是玩偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来水会流到千秋那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过玩偶从灾难手里保护了天秤座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  不愧是幸运物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.98,0:04:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它仿佛就是吸取大地水分的大树一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈别感叹了快点拿东西把水擦干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:47.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个占卜  是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我迟到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子不能进入泳池！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然占卜上是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泳装是蓝色的至少会好点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  禁止利子接近泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是为了什么来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也来泳池了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.09,0:05:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈  你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐约看到些蓝色的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊  幸运色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子  和藤冈一起的话可以进入泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈  利子由于某种理由今天可能会溺水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你说不定可以改变这个命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:12.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈  要紧握住利子的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.79,0:06:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天运气超差？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,占卜什么的真不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.20,0:06:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希和淳子好像在一起打工
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应聘的时候会有面试之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:11.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会做些什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介绍兴趣  特长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.48,0:07:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展示自已的长处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自我PR吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长这种啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长的想法可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来练习吧！练习！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来当面试官问问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来面试  确认你适不适合当面试官
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么千秋适合当面试官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  夏奈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算哪门子自我PR啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点难懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难懂么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再具体点的更简单易懂的美少女就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微失礼一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉变得简单易懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单易懂  合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就合格了啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就交由我来担当面试官了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  维持美少女的模式进行面试吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这么说话有点怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不受理来自对方提出的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.62,0:08:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请自我PR一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.83,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常被人说很开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:06.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田小姐比昨天换下的荧光灯还要明亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋小姐  不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎饼的袋子太坚固了打不开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用剪刀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起面试更不擅长应对美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈先生  今天来访我家的动机是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  动机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南同学打电话邀请我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  邀请什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.09,0:09:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我简直就像是没有礼仪的女子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  她怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,样子好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不受理来自对方提出的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只给你一个提示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是把自己是怎么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考虑些什么传达出去就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你自我PR
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  现在的我满脑子只想做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢平常的南夏奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不听到这句话的话  就一直要演下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.94,0:10:46.94,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～谷  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:51.95,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}恐怖～～沙漠  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们一起去把太平洋游个遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  下海之前要先做准备运动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:12.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来海边要事先我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要做心理准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是穿着泳装么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备地多充分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.57,0:11:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你说穿了过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  今天吉野在场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她面前穿泳装太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:33.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.27,0:11:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野说不定注意到了我的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍不换上泳装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是…不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天似乎有点感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想让阿珍来教我游泳的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:54.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍…稍微休息下就好了  你先游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.00,0:12:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会真希和淳子也会过来汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  千秋她们已经去游了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.25,0:12:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  要涂防晒油吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮你涂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍满脸通红
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.10,0:13:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香到底用了什么绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:31.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要放手  不能放哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  相信我吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.22,0:13:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松身体  只动腿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋可不会游泳  溺水了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想让你们知道大海的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈你是姐姐  做事之前也考虑下后果吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这海参当我道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为阿珍你说不放手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也要一直做朋友哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  刚才谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你喜欢海参吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:57.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你  我和千秋变得要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你邀请我一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能来海边真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到最后都不要松懈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回去之前都是海水浴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工很快就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和春香她们一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  炒面就是要像皮筋一样有嚼劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这微微的焦味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然咖喱有分欧洲和印度等各种风味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.25,0:15:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个是速食咖喱包的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉面要泡得有些糊了再吃才算赚到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说都很难吃咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个说出来就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易来一趟海边  都被你给糟蹋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像都没食欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋好像很失落的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算只有一个人失落
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也开心不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就交给我吧  你们就去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有你这种人去照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才让她误以为这是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是春香把千秋宠坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  说得过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候就一定要说清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋之所以会变得失落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是因为夏奈说得太过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会去理会没有协调性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那么多次要等大家一起切西瓜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚都因为我  害得大家都没怎么吃东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想现在大家可能饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想负起责任把西瓜切好给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事啦  千秋  没有人在生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  反正你就是个好好先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就来玩切西瓜吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:17:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右边  右边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…稍微往左一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.67,0:18:04.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这是…又甜又多汁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粘着沙子的部分尤其好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  应该是难吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不去理会她了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看这晒痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  完美地晒出了泳装的痕迹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是之前和你们去海边的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天之后  我的夏天就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但不能和修一他们去游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗完澡也不能光着身子到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时不能在别人面前露出自己的身体了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.02,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了羞涩的少女呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:01.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有着耻辱晒痕的男子汉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那个创口贴是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊  是之前返校的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去一次校医室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我会一辈子珍惜这个创口贴的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.61,0:19:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不会撕掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了就给我撕掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  也就是说你以真的样子从千秋那里得到创口贴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:44.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你以阿珍的样子贴着同样的创口贴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋就有可能会发现你的真实身份呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之还是先把创口贴撕下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已经决定了绝对不会把这个撕下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是千秋会发现你的真实身份的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍  来玩黑白棋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.54,0:20:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是玩的话  右手背会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么阿珍  要吃饼干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.04,0:20:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个还是要用手的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.68,0:20:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.53,0:20:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创口贴要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍一直对我摆着拒绝的姿势…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}拒\N绝\N的\N姿\N势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.50,0:20:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前去海边的时候明明关系还那么好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她现在已经讨厌我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事  阿珍很珍惜千秋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那个手势
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个姿势一定是像万岁什么的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:05.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去认真确认友情吧  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把手藏起来的话不是这样  而是要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:20.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.36,0:21:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿珍…太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:36.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手就还是…不要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  要我来代替千秋发言的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.81,0:21:48.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是阿珍你这蠢货
